'''Bakrunba Sokono Karajago''' (BSK) walima Bakrunba Sokono Soro (BSS) [Ingliz: GDP (Gross Domestic Products) or GDI (Gross Domestic Income), Franse: PIB (Produits Intérieurs Brutes) ye sumanfen do min be jatelike faso soro ani bofen la jamana do ka soroko la. BSK donnen inafo sugu kima ka karajago labannen bee ani ca kelenw jamana kono wati furance do kono ( akacala san kono). 

Foroba famuyacogo labonba walasa ka (BSK) suman ani k’a famuya ye musakabo sira.

BSK = [[makoɲe]] + [[bakrunba nafololabugun]] + [[fanga ka musakabo]] + [[(laboliw – ladonniw)]] walima 

'''BSK = M+ N + F + (B-D).'''

Sorokodonna [[Keynes]] ka jatela danfara ka sigi makoɲe kuma la min be tila ka ke fan fla ye: kenyereye makoɲe ani foroba ca (walima fanga ) ka musakabo. Nafa fla min be makoɲe tila la ye bonbasɔrɔkodon ta sira fe ye:

'''Kenyereye makonye''' : o ye haminko lakoloma ye lafiya sorokodon na.
